@startuml
title Viaverse Search / Recommendation — Activity Diagram
start
:Query/feed request;
:Parse query + context\nlocale / location / intent;
if (AI assist enabled?) then (yes)
  :AI intent/category suggestion;
endif
:Apply privacy + visibility\napproximate area only;
:Search OpenSearch\ngeo/category/full-text/vector later;
:Filter availability\ncapability / trust / safety;
:Rank candidates\nrelevance + trust + freshness;
:Apply sponsored/native\nonly after gates;
:Apply personalization\nprivacy-safe;
:Return result cards\nreason hints;
:Track impression/click\naggregated analytics;
:Update search quality metrics;
:Emit search/growth events;
stop

note bottom
Exact address/private data never enters public search.
Public search uses service area, approximate geography and approved public profile fields.
end note
@enduml
